I am using maven, why?The main reason is, it has the most standard stuff which works automatically once you do
things the maven way. For a simple webapplication

    Step1: Create a pom with groupId, artifactId and version (packaging: war)
    Step2: Add the required dependencies to the pom
    Step3: move the java sources to src/main/java,resources to src/main/recources and  webapp content to src/main/webapp, test content to src/test/java and src/test/resources
    Step4: set the compiler compliance version using the maven compiler plugin

-elias hasnat

